ter，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多外媒報導tweet都推唔上千rt<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港手足可唔可以都繼續努力，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好浪費國際對中國人權問題及香港的關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出門之前 rt like reply<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=1f8a0377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"af245ea5cf3e06143dd5d10bee79e0f9a0666855","tid":1818490,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"澳洲做嘢都係有部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0d2ed6a49a3e4352a9d671c486a8d7c05390c5","tid":1818490,"uid":82203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"475345ef7a6594e2beb8304e071761bf1151a84c","tid":1818490,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90beebed28e207795d16d46e46f8c335aa787512","tid":1818490,"uid":47110,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"302d03b0c5c1ac83928d155291957a442525bf0c","tid":1818490,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0ce47276ed2d5c0b3cd289e61a2dd